Video footage of a crash on the N3 that claimed a life. Another person was critically injured. 
Video : Supplied


Rescue Care Operations Director, Garrith Jamieson, said when emergency teams arrived at the scene, they found absolute carnage. 

“Two vehicles and a truck had collided before one overturned coming to rest on its roof. One driver had sustained major injuries and unfortunately there was nothing more paramedics could do for him and he was declared deceased on the scene,” Jamieson said. 

He said the second driver had sustained moderate injuries and was stabilised on the scene by Advanced Life Support paramedics before being transported to a nearby Hospital for the further care that he required.

The Mercury